// list_pending.pop
// Demonstrates filtering to show only pending tasks

[] >> tasks.
{"id": 1, "title": "Buy Milk", "done": true} >+> tasks.
{"id": 2, "title": "Read Book", "done": false} >+> tasks.
{"id": 3, "title": "Write Code", "done": true} >+> tasks.
{"id": 4, "title": "Walk Dog", "done": false} >+> tasks.

"--- All Tasks ---" >> Display.
tasks >> Display.

tasks >> Filter:
    @["done"] >> check:
        is false: true.
        else: false.
    ..
.. >> pending_tasks.

"--- Pending Tasks ---" >> Display.
pending_tasks >> Display.
